<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about wifi)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/wifi.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 30 Dec 2017 15:36:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Ubuntu命令行连接wifi</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ubuntuming-ling-xing-lian-jie-wifi/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; cd /usr/local/bin/
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; cd /home/long
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; wpa_passphrase SSID PWD &amp;gt; /home/long/wifi.conf
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo emacs /etc/network/interfaces
auto wlan0
iface wlan0 inet dhcp
wpa-conf /home/long/wifi.conf
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo reboot
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;注意&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;路由器必须要打开DHCP才可以正常连接。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Ubuntu</category><category>wifi</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ubuntuming-ling-xing-lian-jie-wifi/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jul 2017 03:06:54 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>